(b) any faults or defects existing at the time of commencement of this Policy of Insurance of
which the Insured or his Representatives were or ought reasonably to have been aware,
irrespective of whether such faults or defects were known to the Insurer or not;
(c) go-slow, total or partial cessation of work, the Insurer shall not be liable for
(d) loss or damage caused by intentional overloading or experiments involving the
