  <data key="d2">Section – II: All Risks of Physical Loss or Damage / Machinery Insurance
All Machinery and Equipment including electrical or electronic machinery of The
Insured’s plants including spare parts with no specification being the property of
The Insured and all machinery and equipment in which The Insured has an
insurable interest in case of loss or damage covered under this Policy, whilst
contained in The Insured’s Premises and elsewhere as specified in The Schedule.</data>
