  <data key="d3">48</data>
  <data key="d2">Expiration
If this Policy should expire or be cancelled while an insured event affecting the Property
Insured is in progress, it is understood and agreed that Insurers, subject to all other terms,
conditions and exclusions of this Policy, are responsible as if the entire loss had occurred
prior to the expiration of this insurance.</data>
</node>
