  <data key="d2">Loss Payee
Loss is payable to the Insured or as directed by the Insured, which shall include such party
who has an insured interest in the subject matter insured at the time of loss or damage.</data>
</node>
<node id="sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:142">
