  <data key="d1">tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings</data>
  <data key="d3">142</data>
  <data key="d2">Bankruptcy and Insolvency
In the event of bankruptcy or insolvency of the Insured or any entity comprising the
Insured, the Insurer shall not be relieved thereby of the payment of any claims hereunder
because of such bankruptcy or insolvency, except under Section III(All Risk Operational
Business Interruption).</data>
</node>
<node id="sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:144">
  <data key="d0">SENTENCE</data>
  <data key="d1">tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings</data>
  <data key="d3">144</data>
  <data key="d2">Deductibles
This Policy does not cover the amounts of the Deductibles stated in the Schedule in respect
of each and every loss as ascertained after the application of all other terms and conditions
of the Policy including any underinsurance.</data>
</node>
<node id="sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:145">
  <data key="d0">SENTENCE</data>
  <data key="d1">tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings</data>
  <data key="d3">145</data>
  <data key="d2">Warranted that the Insured shall not effect insurance in respect of the amounts of the
Deductibles stated in the Schedule.</data>
</node>
<node id="sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:147">
  <data key="d0">SENTENCE</data>
  <data key="d1">tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings</data>
  <data key="d3">147</data>
  <data key="d2">Reinstatement of Policy Limit
At all times during the Period of Insurance of this Policy, the insurance cover will be
maintained to the full extent of the respective Sum Insured in consideration of which upon
the settlement of any loss under this Policy exceeding the amount specified in The Schedule,
pro-rata Premium for the unexpired period from the date of such loss to the expiry of
Period of Insurance for the amount of such loss shall be payable by the Insured to the
Insurer.</data>
</node>
<node id="sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:148">
  <data key="d0">SENTENCE</data>
  <data key="d1">tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings</data>
  <data key="d3">148</data>
  <data key="d2">The additional Premium referred above shall be deducted from the net claim amount
payable under this Policy.</data>
</node>
<node id="sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:149">
  <data key="d0">SENTENCE</data>
  <data key="d1">tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings</data>
  <data key="d3">149</data>
  <data key="d2">This continuous cover to the full extent will be available
notwithstanding any previous loss for which the Insurer may have paid hereunder and
irrespective of the fact whether the additional Premium as mentioned above has been
actually paid or not following such loss.</data>
</node>
<node id="sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:150">
  <data key="d0">SENTENCE</data>
  <data key="d1">tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings</data>
  <data key="d3">150</data>
  <data key="d2">The intention of this condition is to ensure
continuity of the cover to the Insured subject only to the right of the Insurer for deduction
from the claim amount, when settled, of pro-rata Premium to be calculated from the date of
