  <data key="d0">SENTENCE</data>
  <data key="d1">tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings</data>
  <data key="d3">151</data>
  <data key="d2">Notwithstanding what is stated above, the Sum Insured shall stand reduced by the amount
of loss in case the Insured immediately on occurrence of loss exercises his option not to
reinstate the Sum Insured as above.
1.15.</data>
</node>
