  <data key="d3">152</data>
  <data key="d2">Claims / Payments “on account”
All claims to be paid to the Insured within reasonable time after receipt of satisfactory
documentation and the determination of the quantity of the loss presented by the loss
adjuster(s) and agreed by the Insurer.</data>
</node>
