  <data key="d3">164</data>
  <data key="d2">Earthquake
The Insurers shall not be liable for any loss caused by an earthquake occurring before the
effective date and time of this Policy nor for any loss commencing after the expiration date
and time of this Policy.</data>
</node>
<node id="sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:166">
  <data key="d0">SENTENCE</data>
  <data key="d1">tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings</data>
  <data key="d3">166</data>
  <data key="d2">Any and all losses caused by earthquake shall constitute a single loss hereunder provided
that more that one earthquake shock occurring within any seventy two (72) hour period
during the Period of Insurance of this Policy shall be deemed to be a single earthquake
within the meaning thereof.</data>
</node>
