  <data key="d3">278</data>
  <data key="d2">Indemnification
The indemnity arising out of interest insured shall be in respect of: (a) Gross Profit, the loss
actually sustained during the Indemnity Period resulting from a reduction in turnover
including any Increased Cost of Working or (b) specified standing charges, the amount
actually not earned during the Indemnity Period resulting from a reduction in turnover
including any Increased Cost of Working.</data>
</node>
