  <data key="d3">308</data>
  <data key="d2">In the event of any occurrence of loss or damage which might cause an interruption of
or interference with the Business Insured
i. The Insured shall immediately notify the Insurer and send it written confirmation thereof
within forty-eight hours of the occurrence;
ii.</data>
</node>
