  <data key="d3">316</data>
  <data key="d2">In the event of a claim being made under this section, the Insured shall at his own
expense deliver to the Insurer not later than thirty days after the interruption of or
interference with the Business Insured or within such further periods as the Insurer may
allow in writing a written statement setting forth particulars of the claim.
