  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">containing particulars sufficient to identify the loss and/or damage, claim or suit and also reasonably obtainable information with respect to the time, place and circumstances thereof as well as nature and extent of the loss or damage, and the names and addresses of available witnesses.</data>
