<edge source="ent:written_notice_of_loss_damage_claim_suit" target="ent:names_and_addresses_of_available_witnesses" id="e:rel:30325cc6e27926f8">
  <data key="d26">CONTAINING</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">containing particulars sufficient to identify the loss and/or damage, claim or suit and also reasonably obtainable information with respect to the time, place and circumstances thereof as well as nature and extent of the loss or damage, and the names and addresses of available witnesses.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:if_claim_is_made_or_suit_is_brought_against_the_insured" target="ent:the_insurer_of_every_demand_notice_summons_or_other_process_received_by_him_or_his_representative" id="e:rel:77b378e1bc66e7b4">
  <data key="d26">THE_INSURED_SHALL_AT_THE_EARLIEST_PRACTICABLE_AD</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">if claim is made or suit is brought against the Insured, the Insured shall at the earliest practicable advise the Insurer of every demand, notice, summons or other process received by him or his representative.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:this_clause_e" target="ent:the_provisions_of_the_subrogation_clause" id="e:rel:bbe56977fc8fbce5">
  <data key="d26">SHALL_NOT_OVERRIDE</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">Notwithstanding the foregoing this clause shall not override the provisions of the Subrogation Clause.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:if_the_insured_or_anyone_acting_on_his_behalf_hinders_or_obstructs_the_insurer_in_any_way_or_does_not_comply_with_any_reasonable_recommendations_the_insurer_may_make_following_the_notification_of_any_loss_or_damage" target="ent:forfeited" id="e:rel:4d3a1578951228aa">
  <data key="d26">ALL_BENEFITS_CLAIMED_UNDER_ANY_SECTION_OF_THIS_P</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">If the Insured or anyone acting on his behalf hinders or obstructs the Insurer in any way or does not comply with any reasonable recommendations the Insurer may make following the notification of any loss or damage, all benefits claimed under any Section of this Policy shall be forfeited.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:on_the_happening_of_any_loss_or_damage_to_any_of_the_property_insured_under_this_policy" target="ent:enter_and_take_and_keep_possession_of_the_building_or_premises_where_the_loss_or_damage_has_happened" id="e:rel:3c82fad49b37c716">
  <data key="d26">THE_INSURER_MAY</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">On the happening of any loss or damage to any of the Property Insured under this Policy the Insurer may a. enter and take and keep possession of the building or Premises where the loss or damage has happened</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:on_the_happening_of_any_loss_or_damage_to_any_of_the_property_insured_under_this_policy" target="ent:take_possession_of_or_require_to_be_delivered_to_it_any_property_of_the_insured_in_the_buildings_or_on_the_premises_at_the_time_of_the_loss_or_damage" id="e:rel:c8c4c077358a7f0b">
  <data key="d26">THE_INSURER_MAY</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">b. take possession of or require to be delivered to it any property of the Insured in the buildings or on the Premises at the time of the loss or damage</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:on_the_happening_of_any_loss_or_damage_to_any_of_the_property_insured_under_this_policy" target="ent:keep_possession_of_any_such_property_and_examine_sort_arrange_remove_or_otherwise_deal_with_the_same" id="e:rel:6e7d6ea24bf8c627">
  <data key="d26">THE_INSURER_MAY</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">c. keep possession of any such property and examine, sort, arrange, remove or otherwise deal with the same</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:on_the_happening_of_any_loss_or_damage_to_any_of_the_property_insured_under_this_policy" target="ent:sell_any_such_property_or_dispose_of_the_same_for_account_of_whom_it_may_concern" id="e:rel:4b1e5117324b666c">
  <data key="d26">THE_INSURER_MAY</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:112</data>
  <data key="d38">d. sell any such property or dispose of the same for account of whom it may concern.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:the_powers_conferred_by_this_condition" target="ent:notice_in_writing_is_given_by_the_insured_that_he_makes_no_claim_under_this_policy_or_if_any_claim_is_made_until_such_claim_is_finally_determined_or_withdrawn" id="e:rel:49270029fe07f7a9">
  <data key="d26">CAN_BE_EXERCISED_BY_THE_INSURER_AT_ANY_TIME_UNTI</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">The powers conferred by this condition can be exercised by the Insurer at any time until notice in writing is given by the Insured that he makes no claim under this Policy or, if any claim is made, until such claim is finally determined or withdrawn</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:if_the_insured_or_any_person_acting_on_his_behalf_shall_not_comply_with_the_requirements_of_the_insurer_or_shall_hinder_or_obstruct_the_insurer_in_the_exercise_of_its_powers_hereunder" target="ent:forfeited" id="e:rel:54e0203841e0a0e3">
  <data key="d26">ALL_BENEFIT_UNDER_THIS_POLICY_SHALL_BE</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">If the Insured or any person acting on his behalf shall not comply with the requirements of the Insurer or shall hinder or obstruct the Insurer in the exercise of its powers hereunder, all benefit under this Policy shall be forfeited.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:upon_notifying_the_insurer" target="ent:repair_any_minor_damage_or_replace_any_parts_of_the_property_insured_that_have_sustained_minor_damage" id="e:rel:ad71846a0028fdc3">
  <data key="d26">THE_INSURED_MAY</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">Upon notifying the Insurer the Insured may repair any minor damage or replace any parts of the Property Insured that have sustained minor damage.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:in_all_other_cases" target="ent:inspect_the_loss_or_damage_before_any_repairs_are_effected" id="e:rel:b43d301432d3fcd3">
  <data key="d26">THE_INSURERS_AGENT_SHALL_BE_GIVEN_THE_OPPORTUNIT</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">In all other cases The Insurer’s Agent shall be given the opportunity to inspect the loss or damage before any repairs are effected</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:if_the_insurer_s_agent_does_not_carry_out_the_inspection_within_a_period_of_time_which_could_be_considered_reasonable_under_the_circumstances" target="ent:proceed_with_the_repair_or_replacement" id="e:rel:8f82919c97d47f92">
  <data key="d26">THE_INSURED_SHALL_BE_ENTITLED_TO</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">and if the Insurer’s Agent does not carry out the inspection within a period of time which could be considered reasonable under the circumstances, the Insured shall be entitled to proceed with the repair or replacement.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:in_the_event_of_accidental_physical_loss_or_damage_to_the_property_insured_hereunder" target="ent:accept_repair_or_replacement_terms_as_offered_by_the_original_equipment_manufacturer_oem" id="e:rel:eec6b0e7a19a533c">
  <data key="d26">THE_INSURED_SHALL_HAVE_THE_OPTION_TO</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">It is further noted and agreed that in the event of accidental physical loss or damage to the Property Insured hereunder the Insured, at sole discretion, shall have the option to accept repair or replacement terms as offered by the Original Equipment Manufacturer (OEM) regardless of any other terms offered from other suppliers, manufacturers or fabricators.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:the_difference_between_the_oem_quote_and_the_lowest_quote" target="ent:25_of_the_lowest_quote" id="e:rel:cf7fc8e3fa126743">
  <data key="d26">DOES_NOT_EXCEED</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">Provided always that the difference between the OEM quote and the lowest quote does not exceed 25% of the lowest quote and quotes are based on same technological specifications.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:quotes" target="ent:same_technological_specifications" id="e:rel:b33d796dab867d70">
  <data key="d26">ARE_BASED_ON</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">Provided always that the difference between the OEM quote and the lowest quote does not exceed 25% of the lowest quote and quotes are based on same technological specifications.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:spares_currently_insured_hereunder_and_represented_within_the_total_sum_insured_under_the_policy_of_insurance_becoming_obsolete_following_an_indemnifiable_loss_to_the_unit_and_or_units_to_which_they_belong" target="ent:constructive_total_loss" id="e:rel:36cd6888a50d7408">
  <data key="d26">SHALL_ALSO_BE_DEEMED_A</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">In the event of spares currently insured hereunder and represented within the total Sum Insured under the Policy of Insurance becoming obsolete following an indemnifiable loss to the unit and/or units to which they belong such spare parts shall also be deemed a constructive total loss provided always that such parts cannot be used as spares for any other units within the Premises of the Insured.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:obsolete_spare_parts" target="ent:such_parts_cannot_be_used_as_spares_for_any_other_units_within_the_premises_of_the_insured" id="e:rel:44dc6612ab7832e9">
  <data key="d26">PROVIDED_THAT</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">provided always that such parts cannot be used as spares for any other units within the Premises of the Insured.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:the_salvage_of_any_insured_property_on_the_occurrence_of_any_loss_or_damage_herein" target="ent:the_insurer_subject_to_indemnification_of_the_insured_in_full" id="e:rel:6716660db2cad65c">
  <data key="d26">SHALL_ACCRUE_TO</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">The salvage of any insured property on the occurrence of any loss or damage herein shall accrue to the Insurer (subject to indemnification of the Insured in full).</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:in_case_of_loss_or_damage_to_property_bearing_a_brand_or_trademark_or_the_name_of_the_insured" target="ent:removal_in_the_customary_manner_of_all_such_brands_or_trademarks_or_other_identifying_characteristics" id="e:rel:a49ca578b70161f5">
  <data key="d26">THE_SALVAGE_VALUE_OF_SUCH_DAMAGED_PROPERTY_SHALL</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">In case of loss or damage to property bearing a brand or trademark, or the name of the Insured, which in any way carries or implies the guarantee or the responsibility of the manufacturer or the Insured, the salvage value of such damaged property shall be determined after removal in the customary manner of all such brands or trademarks or other identifying characteristics.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:the_insured_exercising_reasonable_discretion" target="ent:the_sole_judge_as_to_whether_the_goods_involved_in_any_loss_under_this_policy_are_fit_for_consumption" id="e:rel:2edd7d377e102451">
  <data key="d26">SHALL_BE</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">The Insured, exercising reasonable discretion, shall be the sole judge as to whether the goods involved in any loss under this Policy are fit for consumption</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:no_goods_so_deemed_by_the_insured_to_be_unfit_for_consumption" target="ent:the_insured_or_with_the_insured_s_consent" id="e:rel:f6a06a640b329524">
  <data key="d26">SHALL_BE_SOLD_OR_OTHERWISE_DISPOSED_OF_EXCEPT_BY</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">and no goods so deemed by the Insured to be unfit for consumption shall be sold or otherwise disposed of except by the Insured or with the Insured’s consent</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:if_the_property_hereby_insured_shall_at_the_commencement_of_any_damage_be_collectively_of_greater_value_than_the_sum_insured_thereon" target="ent:his_own_insurer_for_the_difference" id="e:rel:21f11f508ee359bc">
  <data key="d26">THEN_THE_INSURED_SHALL_BE_CONSIDERED_AS_BEING</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">If the property hereby insured shall, at the commencement of any damage, be collectively of greater value than the Sum Insured thereon, then the Insured shall be considered as being his own insurer for the difference, and shall bear the rateable proportion of the loss accordingly.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:salvage" target="ent:the_same_proportion" id="e:rel:972223dee4a1e105">
  <data key="d26">IS_TO_BE_CONSIDERED_IN</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:134</data>
  <data key="d38">Salvage is to be considered in the same proportion.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:every_item_if_more_than_one_of_the_policy" target="ent:this_condition_underinsurance" id="e:rel:9bdca328a149195d">
  <data key="d26">SHALL_BE_SEPARATELY_SUBJECT_TO</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">Every item, if more than one, of the Policy shall be separately subject to this condition.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:if_at_the_time_of_any_loss_or_damage_occurrence_to_any_property_hereby_insured_there_be_any_other_subsisting_insurance_or_insurances" target="ent:its_rateable_proportion_of_such_loss_or_damage" id="e:rel:3ef278c4974bbafc">
  <data key="d26">THE_INSURER_SHALL_NOT_BE_LIABLE_TO_PAY_OR_CONTRI</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">If at the time of any loss or damage occurrence to any property hereby insured, there be any other subsisting insurance or insurances whether effected by the Insured or by any other person or persons, covering either such loss or any part of it or the same property the Insurer shall not be liable to pay or contribute more than its rateable proportion of such loss or damage.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:loss" target="ent:the_insured_or_as_directed_by_the_insured" id="e:rel:a928f627ac545b0c">
  <data key="d26">IS_PAYABLE_TO</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">Loss is payable to the Insured or as directed by the Insured, which shall include such party who has an insured interest in the subject matter insured at the time of loss or damage.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:loss_payee" target="ent:such_party_who_has_an_insured_interest_in_the_subject_matter_insured_at_the_time_of_loss_or_damage" id="e:rel:f048120f382cc265">
  <data key="d26">SHALL_INCLUDE</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">Loss is payable to the Insured or as directed by the Insured, which shall include such party who has an insured interest in the subject matter insured at the time of loss or damage.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:in_the_event_of_bankruptcy_or_insolvency_of_the_insured_or_any_entity_comprising_the_insured" target="ent:except_under_section_iii_all_risk_operational_business_interruption" id="e:rel:246cca0923fab1f2">
  <data key="d26">THE_INSURER_SHALL_NOT_BE_RELIEVED_THEREBY_OF_THE</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">In the event of bankruptcy or insolvency of the Insured or any entity comprising the Insured, the Insurer shall not be relieved thereby of the payment of any claims hereunder because of such bankruptcy or insolvency, except under Section III(All Risk Operational Business Interruption).</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:at_all_times_during_the_period_of_insurance_of_this_policy" target="ent:the_full_extent_of_the_respective_sum_insured" id="e:rel:45db97a4bcb2ab75">
  <data key="d26">THE_INSURANCE_COVER_WILL_BE_MAINTAINED_TO</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">At all times during the Period of Insurance of this Policy, the insurance cover will be maintained to the full extent of the respective Sum Insured</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:upon_the_settlement_of_any_loss_under_this_policy_exceeding_the_amount_specified_in_the_schedule" target="ent:the_insured_to_the_insurer" id="e:rel:f496accc93aca86f">
  <data key="d26">PRORATA_PREMIUM_FOR_THE_UNEXPIRED_PERIOD_FROM_TH</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">in consideration of which upon the settlement of any loss under this Policy exceeding the amount specified in The Schedule, pro-rata Premium for the unexpired period from the date of such loss to the expiry of Period of Insurance for the amount of such loss shall be payable by the Insured to the Insurer.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:the_additional_premium_referred_above" target="ent:the_net_claim_amount_payable_under_this_policy" id="e:rel:846f98a3d88f4405">
  <data key="d26">SHALL_BE_DEDUCTED_FROM</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">The additional Premium referred above shall be deducted from the net claim amount payable under this Policy.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:continuous_cover_to_the_full_extent" target="ent:any_previous_loss_for_which_the_insurer_may_have_paid_hereunder_and_irrespective_of_the_fact_whether_the_additional_premium_as_mentioned_above_has_been_actually_paid_or_not_following_such_loss" id="e:rel:3f466aa4d57e807e">
  <data key="d26">WILL_BE_AVAILABLE_NOTWITHSTANDING</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">This continuous cover to the full extent will be available notwithstanding any previous loss for which the Insurer may have paid hereunder and irrespective of the fact whether the additional Premium as mentioned above has been actually paid or not following such loss.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:the_intention_of_this_condition" target="ent:continuity_of_the_cover_to_the_insured_subject_only_to_the_right_of_the_insurer_for_deduction_from_the_claim_amount_when_settled_of_pro_rata_premium_to_be_calculated_from_the_date_of_loss_till_expiry_of_this_policy" id="e:rel:ec38b31292867cb6">
  <data key="d26">IS_TO_ENSURE</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">The intention of this condition is to ensure continuity of the cover to the Insured subject only to the right of the Insurer for deduction from the claim amount, when settled, of pro-rata Premium to be calculated from the date of loss till expiry of this Policy.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:the_sum_insured" target="ent:the_amount_of_loss_in_case_the_insured_immediately_on_occurrence_of_loss_exercises_his_option_not_to_reinstate_the_sum_insured_as_above" id="e:rel:2843b74d12a5ec87">
  <data key="d26">SHALL_STAND_REDUCED_BY</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">Notwithstanding what is stated above, the Sum Insured shall stand reduced by the amount of loss in case the Insured immediately on occurrence of loss exercises his option not to reinstate the Sum Insured as above.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:all_claims" target="ent:reasonable_time_after_receipt_of_satisfactory_documentation_and_the_determination_of_the_quantity_of_the_loss_presented_by_the_loss_adjuster_s_and_agreed_by_the_insurer" id="e:rel:f0d9ba71a3e28cca">
  <data key="d26">TO_BE_PAID_TO_THE_INSURED_WITHIN</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">All claims to be paid to the Insured within reasonable time after receipt of satisfactory documentation and the determination of the quantity of the loss presented by the loss adjuster(s) and agreed by the Insurer.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:in_the_event_of_indemnifiable_loss_or_damage" target="ent:this_is_approved_by_the_insurer_and_where_the_liability_of_the_insurer_has_been_established_in_a_preliminary_loss_report_and_accepted_by_the_insurer" id="e:rel:796102a5415c0f5b">
  <data key="d26">PAYMENT_ON_ACCOUNT_WILL_BE_MADE_BY_THE_INSURER_A</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">In the event of indemnifiable loss or damage, payment “on account” will be made by the Insurer as early as possible on request if this is approved by the Insurer and where the liability of the Insurer has been established in a preliminary loss report and accepted by the Insurer.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:claim_payments" target="ent:the_same_currency_as_premium_received_by_the_insurer" id="e:rel:7ddd8cfbd4ab04a9">
  <data key="d26">SHALL_BE_MADE_IN</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:156</data>
  <data key="d38">Claim payments shall be made in the same currency as Premium received by the Insurer.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:if_exchange_rates_are_to_be_applicable" target="ent:the_one_specified_in_the_london_financial_times_for_the_date_of_premium_received_by_the_insurer" id="e:rel:faaaa4bb041b9fcd">
  <data key="d26">THE_EXCHANGE_RATE_WILL_BE</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">If exchange rates are to be applicable, the exchange rate will be the one specified in the London Financial Times for the date of Premium received by the Insurer.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:liability_for_windstorm_losses_after_expiration" target="ent:the_first_windstorm_damage_occurs_prior_to_the_date_and_time_of_the_expiration_of_this_policy" id="e:rel:526e0fa1e70dd7af">
  <data key="d26">PROVIDED_THAT</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">provided that the first windstorm damage occurs prior to the date and time of the expiration of this Policy.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:each_loss_by_windstorm" target="ent:a_single_claim_hereunder" id="e:rel:13d3dc31f9a44ec7">
  <data key="d26">SHALL_CONSTITUTE</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">Each loss by windstorm shall constitute a single claim hereunder; provided, if more than one windstorm shall occur within any period of seventy two (72) hours during the term of this Policy such windstorm shall be deemed to be a single windstorm within the meaning thereof.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:if_more_than_one_windstorm_shall_occur_within_any_period_of_seventy_two_72_hours_during_the_term_of_this_policy" target="ent:a_single_windstorm" id="e:rel:287066cac37a0306">
  <data key="d26">SUCH_WINDSTORM_SHALL_BE_DEEMED_TO_BE</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">if more than one windstorm shall occur within any period of seventy two (72) hours during the term of this Policy such windstorm shall be deemed to be a single windstorm within the meaning thereof.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:official_recognized_authority_or_as_agreed_between_the_insurer_and_the_insured" target="ent:the_moment_from_which_each_of_the_aforesaid_periods_of_seventy_two_72_hours_shall_be_deemed_to_have_commenced" id="e:rel:457f761f950d8b47">
  <data key="d26">WILL_ELECT</data>
