</edge>
<edge source="ent:liability_for_loss_or_damage_after_24_months" target="ent:otherwise_agreed_in_writing_or_the_claim_is_submitted_to_a_court_or_arbitration_panel_within_the_time_prescribed_therefore_in_accordance_with_applicable_law" id="e:rel:f4a54f2acf134e66">
  <data key="d26">UNLESS</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">unless otherwise agreed in writing or the claim is submitted to a court or arbitration panel within the time prescribed therefore in accordance with applicable law.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:any_action_or_proceeding_against_them_for_the_recovery_of_any_claim_under_or_by_virtue_of_this_insurance" target="ent:commenced_within_the_time_prescribed_therefore_in_accordance_with_applicable_law" id="e:rel:972cd6fe28aefd66">
  <data key="d26">SHALL_NOT_BE_BARRED_IF</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">The Insurer agrees that any action or proceeding against them for the recovery of any claim under or by virtue of this insurance shall not be barred if commenced within the time prescribed therefore in accordance with applicable law.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:if_the_insurer_disclaims_liability_in_respect_of_any_claim_and_if_conciliation_is_not_commenced_within_12_twelve_months_of_such_a_disclaimer" target="ent:forfeited" id="e:rel:370d9b2b30021109">
  <data key="d26">ALL_BENEFITS_UNDER_THIS_POLICY_OF_INSURANCE_IN_R</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">If the Insurer disclaims liability in respect of any claim and if conciliation is not commenced within 12 (twelve) months of such a disclaimer, all benefits under this Policy of Insurance in respect of that claim shall be forfeited.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:if_there_is_a_partial_reimbursement" target="ent:the_amount_settled" id="e:rel:a64fe9487d393a76">
  <data key="d26">SUBROGATION_TO_BE_RESTRICTED_TO</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:181</data>
  <data key="d38">- if there is a partial reimbursement, subrogation to be restricted to the amount settled.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:except_as_specifically_provided_or_permitted_by_this_policy" target="ent:waive_release_or_diminish_rights_of_recovery_or_subrogation_with_respect_to_any_claim" id="e:rel:4dd0026edc434b79">
  <data key="d26">THE_INSURED_SHALL_NOT</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">Except as specifically provided or permitted by this Policy, the Insured shall not waive, release or diminish rights of recovery or subrogation with respect to any claim which, upon payment thereof by Insurers, would otherwise belong or accrue Insurers, and insofar as and to the extent that any action by the Insured waives, releases or diminishes the rights of recovery or subrogation in respect of such claim, the Insured shall have no liability under this Policy.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:insofar_as_and_to_the_extent_that_any_action_by_the_insured_waives_releases_or_diminishes_the_rights_of_recovery_or_subrogation_in_respect_of_such_claim" target="ent:no_liability_under_this_policy" id="e:rel:6977b6bdda26450b">
  <data key="d26">THE_INSURED_SHALL_HAVE</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">and insofar as and to the extent that any action by the Insured waives, releases or diminishes the rights of recovery or subrogation in respect of such claim, the Insured shall have no liability under this Policy.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:if_any_dispute_or_difference_shall_arise_as_to_the_quantum_to_be_paid_under_this_policy_liability_being_otherwise_admitted" target="ent:the_decision_of_a_sole_arbitrator_to_be_appointed_in_writing_by_the_parties" id="e:rel:00115d1fecc4c20e">
  <data key="d26">SUCH_DIFFERENCE_SHALL_INDEPENDENTLY_OF_ALL_OTHER</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">If any dispute or difference shall arise as to the quantum to be paid under this policy (liability being otherwise admitted) such difference shall independently of all other questions be referred to the decision of a sole arbitrator to be appointed in writing by the parties to or if they cannot agree upon a single arbitrator within 30 days of any party invoking arbitration, the same shall be referred to a panel of three arbitrators, comprising of two arbitrators, one to be appointed by each of the parties to the dispute/difference and the third arbitrator to be appointed by such two arbitrators and arbitration shall be conducted under and in accordance with the provisions of the Arbitration and Conciliation Act, 1996.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:if_parties_cannot_agree_upon_a_single_arbitrator_within_30_days_of_any_party_invoking_arbitration" target="ent:a_panel_of_three_arbitrators" id="e:rel:431c09c11afaec02">
  <data key="d26">THE_SAME_SHALL_BE_REFERRED_TO</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">if they cannot agree upon a single arbitrator within 30 days of any party invoking arbitration, the same shall be referred to a panel of three arbitrators, comprising of two arbitrators, one to be appointed by each of the parties to the dispute/difference and the third arbitrator to be appointed by such two arbitrators</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:arbitration" target="ent:the_provisions_of_the_arbitration_and_conciliation_act_1996" id="e:rel:faaa6768d03feb06">
  <data key="d26">SHALL_BE_CONDUCTED_UNDER_AND_IN_ACCORDANCE_WITH</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">and arbitration shall be conducted under and in accordance with the provisions of the Arbitration and Conciliation Act, 1996.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:no_difference_or_dispute" target="ent:if_the_company_has_disputed_or_not_accepted_liability_under_or_in_respect_of_this_policy" id="e:rel:1f87b5d4482385cd">
  <data key="d26">SHALL_BE_REFERABLE_TO_ARBITRATION_AS_HEREINBEFOR</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">It is clearly agreed and understood that no difference or dispute shall be referable to arbitration as hereinbefore provided, if the Company has disputed or not accepted liability under or in respect of this policy.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:it_shall_be_a_condition_precedent_to_any_right_of_action_or_suit_upon_this_policy_that" target="ent:first_obtained" id="e:rel:c0d0466ceec90fde">
  <data key="d26">THE_AWARD_BY_SUCH_ARBITRATOR_ARBITRATORS_OF_THE_</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">It is hereby expressly stipulated and declared that it shall be a condition precedent to any right of action or suit upon this policy that the award by such arbitrator/ arbitrators of the amount of the loss or damage shall be first obtained.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:nothing_herein_contained" target="ent:the_force_of_the_arbitration_clause_above" id="e:rel:f765072623153b23">
  <data key="d26">SHALL_BE_HELD_TO_DETRACT_FROM</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">but nothing herein contained shall be held to detract from the force of the arbitration clause above.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
