  <data key="d38">This Section does not cover damage to any Property Insured under this Section caused directly or indirectly by or in connection with or arising from or occasioned through : (a) wearing away or wearing out of any part of any Property Insured caused by or naturally resulting from ordinary use or work such as cavitation, erosion, corrosion, rust or due to any gradual deterioration caused by atmospheric conditions or due to other causes</data>
