<edge source="ent:in_the_event_of_loss_or_damage_to_the_property_insured" target="ent:the_cost_of_replacing_or_reinstating_the_insured_property_or_other_property_as_the_insured_may_require" id="e:rel:3b054f449669c2c6">
  <data key="d26">THE_INSURANCE_BENEFITS_IN_RESPECT_THEREOF_SHALL_</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">At the option of the Insured in the event of loss or damage to the Property Insured the insurance benefits in respect thereof shall be based on the cost of replacing or reinstating the Insured property or other property as the Insured may require.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:the_liability_of_the_insurer" target="ent:the_cost_of_replacing_or_reinstating_the_property_with_property_of_a_substantially_similar_kind_and_type_not_being_superior_to_or_more_extensive_than_the_insured_property_when_new" id="e:rel:094cde4dea390009">
  <data key="d26">SHALL_NOT_EXCEED</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">Provided that the liability of the Insurer shall not exceed the cost of replacing or reinstating the property with property of a substantially similar kind and type not being superior to or more extensive than the Insured property when new.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:the_work_of_replacement_or_reinstatement" target="ent:reasonable_dispatch" id="e:rel:b7038dde83810456">
  <data key="d26">MUST_BE_COMMENCED_AND_CARRIED_OUT_WITH</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">The work of replacement or reinstatement (which may be carried out upon another site and in any manner suitable to the requirements of the Insured subject to the liability of the Company not being thereby increased) must be commenced and carried out with reasonable dispatch and in any case must be completed within 12 months after the destruction or damage or within such further time as the Company may in writing allow, otherwise no payment beyond the amount which would have been payable under the Policy if this memorandum had not been incorporated therein shall be made.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:the_work_of_replacement_or_reinstatement" target="ent:12_months_after_the_destruction_or_damage_or_within_such_further_time_as_the_company_may_in_writing_allow" id="e:rel:899fe7b8d1596b51">
  <data key="d26">MUST_BE_COMPLETED_WITHIN</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">The work of replacement or reinstatement (which may be carried out upon another site and in any manner suitable to the requirements of the Insured subject to the liability of the Company not being thereby increased) must be commenced and carried out with reasonable dispatch and in any case must be completed within 12 months after the destruction or damage or within such further time as the Company may in writing allow, otherwise no payment beyond the amount which would have been payable under the Policy if this memorandum had not been incorporated therein shall be made.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:if_the_work_of_replacement_or_reinstatement_is_not_completed_within_the_specified_time" target="ent:made" id="e:rel:057cbb731a9afe73">
  <data key="d26">NO_PAYMENT_BEYOND_THE_AMOUNT_WHICH_WOULD_HAVE_BE</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">otherwise no payment beyond the amount which would have been payable under the Policy if this memorandum had not been incorporated therein shall be made.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:where_for_any_reason_it_is_not_possible_or_if_the_insured_elects_not_to_rebuild_or_replace" target="ent:the_actual_cash_value_of_the_property_at_the_time_of_loss" id="e:rel:fa9ab62267d37e04">
  <data key="d26">THE_INSURER_WILL_PAY_TO_THE_INSURED</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">Where for any reason, it is not possible or if the Insured elects not to rebuild or replace, the Insurer will pay to the Insured the Actual Cash Value of the property at the time of Loss.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:if_the_property_insured_shall_at_the_time_of_reinstatement_replacement_repair_following_a_loss_or_damage_indemnifiable_under_the_policy_be_of_greater_value_than_the_sum_insured_under_the_policy" target="ent:his_own_insurer_for_the_difference_and_shall_bear_a_rateable_proportion_of_loss" id="e:rel:f5553d66c4f04566">
  <data key="d26">THEN_THE_INSURED_SHALL_BE_CONSIDERED_AS_BEING</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">If the Property Insured shall at the time of reinstatement/replacement repair following a loss or damage indemnifiable under the Policy be of greater value than the Sum Insured under the Policy, then the Insured shall be considered as being his own insurer for the difference and shall bear a rateable proportion of loss.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:each_item_of_the_policy_to_which_this_condition_applies" target="ent:the_foregoing_provision_underinsurance_in_section_i" id="e:rel:304f94d0756bc501">
  <data key="d26">SHALL_BE_SEPARATELY_SUBJECT_TO</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">Each item of the Policy to which this condition applies shall be separately subject to the foregoing provision.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:claims" target="ent:actual_cash_value_on_finished_goods_feedstock_chemicals_stores_and_spares_and_other_insured_stock_and_work_in_progress" id="e:rel:00729d5936a6b7d4">
  <data key="d26">ARE_TO_BE_SETTLED_ON</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">Claims are to be settled on Actual Cash Value on finished goods, feedstock, chemicals, stores and spares and other insured stock and work in progress.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:where_feed_stock_chemicals_and_stores_and_spares_are_not_replaced_by_item_of_specification_same_as_the_one_lost_or_damaged_but_by_an_item_of_inferior_quality_specification_for_operating_reasons_or_other_reasons" target="ent:like_items_which_were_lost_or_damaged_based_on_prices_prevailing_at_the_time_of_damage_loss" id="e:rel:1884af482ce85b7b">
  <data key="d26">THE_INSURED_WILL_BE_INDEMNIFIED_AS_IF_HE_HAD_REP</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">Where feed stock chemicals and stores and spares are not replaced by item of specification same as the one lost or damaged, but by an item of inferior quality / specification for operating reasons or other reasons, the Insured will be indemnified as if he had replaced like items which were lost or damaged, based on prices prevailing at the time of damage / loss.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:any_financial_loss_caused_by_the_use_of_items_of_inferior_quality" target="ent:covered" id="e:rel:f4c9c0d3f0db140d">
  <data key="d26">IS_NOT</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">Any financial loss caused by the use of items of inferior quality is not covered.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:with_respect_to_catalysts_lost_or_damaged" target="ent:the_actual_cash_value_at_the_time_of_the_loss_as_per_endorsement" id="e:rel:82177ae3fb0ac6c4">
  <data key="d26">THE_BASIS_OF_INDEMNITY_IS</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">With respect to catalysts lost or damaged, the basis of indemnity if cover is endorsed to this Policy of Insurance is the Actual Cash Value at the time of the loss as per endorsement.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:where_the_assets_damaged_or_lost_are_those_for_which_the_insured_is_only_contractually_liable_for_maintenance" target="ent:the_same_as_above_irrespective_of_any_contract_to_the_contrary" id="e:rel:9af1edba8200ab32">
  <data key="d26">THE_BASIS_OF_INDEMNITY_SHALL_STILL_REMAIN</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">Where the Assets damaged or lost are those for which the Insured is only contractually liable for maintenance, the basis of indemnity shall still remain the same as above, irrespective of any contract to the contrary.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:in_no_event" target="ent:the_total_value_of_property_insured_herein_as_per_the_schedule" id="e:rel:b57301c1107a54c0">
  <data key="d26">SHALL_THE_INSURERS_LIABILITY_ARISING_FROM_ANY_ON</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">In no event shall the Insurer’s liability arising from any one accident or occurrence exceed the total value of Property Insured herein as per the Schedule.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:each_loss_or_series_of_losses" target="ent:separately" id="e:rel:11350280d0e7292c">
  <data key="d26">SHALL_BE_ADJUSTED</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">Each loss or series of losses shall be adjusted separately and from the amount of each such adjusted loss the sum stated as the Deductible in the Schedule shall be deducted.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:from_the_amount_of_each_such_adjusted_loss" target="ent:deducted" id="e:rel:12bed50d1c393b79">
  <data key="d26">THE_SUM_STATED_AS_THE_DEDUCTIBLE_IN_THE_SCHEDULE</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">and from the amount of each such adjusted loss the sum stated as the Deductible in the Schedule shall be deducted.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:section_ii_all_risk_machinery_insurance" target="ent:all_machinery_and_equipment_including_electrical_or_electronic_machinery_of_the_insured_s_plants_and_spare_parts_with_no_specification_being_the_property_of_the_insured" id="e:rel:aeac77d2dbe818d2">
  <data key="d26">INSURES</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">This Section insures the following property: All Machinery and Equipment including electrical or electronic machinery of The Insured’s plants and spare parts with no specification being the property of the Insured and all machinery and equipment in which the Insured has an insurable interest in the Premises of the Insured and elsewhere as specified in the Schedule.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:section_ii_all_risk_machinery_insurance" target="ent:all_machinery_and_equipment_in_which_the_insured_has_an_insurable_interest" id="e:rel:3cb03199d9cee480">
  <data key="d26">INSURES</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">This Section insures the following property: All Machinery and Equipment including electrical or electronic machinery of The Insured’s plants and spare parts with no specification being the property of the Insured and all machinery and equipment in which the Insured has an insurable interest in the Premises of the Insured and elsewhere as specified in the Schedule.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:the_premises_of_the_insured_and_elsewhere_as_specified_in_the_schedule" target="comm_l0:0" id="e:comm_member:1126">
  <data key="d26">MEMBER_OF</data>
  <data key="d39">0</data>
  <data key="d40">0</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:accidental_physical_damage_to_machinery_and_or_equipment_insured" target="ent:such_machinery_and_or_equipment_insured_needing_to_be_repaired_or_replaced" id="e:rel:380181d60c664542">
  <data key="d26">RESULTS_IN</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">which results in such machinery and/or equipment insured needing to be repaired or replaced.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:accident" target="ent:unforeseen_and_fortuitously_manifested_and_or_occurred_physical_damage_including_electrical_breakdown_and_boiler_explosion_to_the_machinery_and_or_equipment_described_above_or_thereof_from_any_cause_not_excluded" id="e:rel:40726c13aa26eba5">
  <data key="d26">SHALL_MEAN</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">Accident shall mean unforeseen and fortuitously manifested and/or occurred physical damage including Electrical Breakdown and Boiler Explosion to the machinery and/or equipment described above or thereof from any cause not excluded</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:accident" target="ent:while_it_is_at_work_or_at_rest_or_during_testing" id="e:rel:5fedcb5ffe8f867e">
  <data key="d26">OCCURS</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:225</data>
  <data key="d38">(a) while it is at work or at rest or during testing</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:accident" target="ent:while_being_dismantled_for_the_purpose_of_cleaning_inspection_and_overhauling_or_removal_to_another_position_or_in_the_course_of_these_operations_themselves_or_subsequent_re_erection_within_the_premises_of_the_insured_or_elsewhere" id="e:rel:6ae7c3b64a037042">
  <data key="d26">OCCURS</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">(b) while being dismantled for the purpose of cleaning, inspection and overhauling or removal to another position or in the course of these operations themselves or subsequent re-erection within the Premises of the Insured or elsewhere.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:this_exclusion_excluded_property_section_ii" target="ent:damage_to_these_parts_only_is_part_of_a_loss_and_or_damage_to_an_insured_machine" id="e:rel:2f9ffdef7669d6ee">
  <data key="d26">SHALL_NOT_BE_APPLICABLE_WHEN</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">this exclusion shall not be applicable when damage to these parts only is part of a loss and/or damage to an insured machine,</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:this_exclusion_excluded_property_section_ii" target="ent:these_parts_and_not_to_any_resulting_damage_to_the_machinery_insured_under_this_section_of_the_policy_of_insurance" id="e:rel:d3a712bee3dfecf9">
  <data key="d26">SHALL_ONLY_REFER_TO</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">this exclusion shall only refer to these parts and not to any resulting damage to the machinery insured under this Section of the Policy of Insurance;</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:this_exclusion_excluded_property_section_ii" target="ent:coverage_under_section_iv_arising_as_a_result_of_such_loss_or_damage" id="e:rel:cfa8f7365deee39d">
  <data key="d26">SHALL_NOT_EXCLUDE</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">for the exceptions mentioned above this exclusion shall not exclude coverage under Section IV arising as a result of such loss or damage.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:electrical_cables_and_instrumentation_cables" target="ent:this_clause_excluded_property_section_ii" id="e:rel:25ef8aa5200187b2">
  <data key="d26">ARE_NOT_EXCLUDED_IN</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:226</data>
  <data key="d38">electrical cables and instrumentation cables are not excluded in this clause</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:this_exclusion_special_exclusions_to_section_ii" target="ent:the_items_immediately_affected" id="e:rel:4954fd7df5865982">
  <data key="d26">SHALL_BE_LIMITED_TO</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">but this exclusion shall be limited to the items immediately affected and shall not exclude liability for loss or damage not otherwise excluded to other parts of the Property Insured as a consequence thereof;</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:this_exclusion_special_exclusions_to_section_ii" target="ent:liability_for_loss_or_damage_not_otherwise_excluded_to_other_parts_of_the_property_insured_as_a_consequence_thereof" id="e:rel:427f26198eb15058">
  <data key="d26">SHALL_NOT_EXCLUDE</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">and shall not exclude liability for loss or damage not otherwise excluded to other parts of the Property Insured as a consequence thereof;</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:loss_or_damage_caused_by_intentional_overloading_or_experiments_involving_the_imposition_of_abnormal_conditions" target="ent:conditions_permitted_by_the_manufacturers_or_by_judgement_of_a_competent_engineer_or_where_such_conditions_arise_during_normal_periodic_testing_including_precommissioning_start_up_and_commissions_of_construction_and_or_erection_projects_insured_under_this_section" id="e:rel:0220c5a902d60306">
  <data key="d26">IS_COVERED_IF</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">except for conditions permitted by the manufacturers or by judgement of a competent engineer or where such conditions arise during normal periodic testing, including precommissioning start-up and commissions of Construction and / or erection Projects insured under this section.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:this_exclusion_loss_or_damage_for_which_manufacturer_supplier_responsible" target="ent:loss_or_damage_caused_in_the_course_of_reinstating_or_replacing_an_otherwise_insured_damage" id="e:rel:12a6d60ffce18aa0">
  <data key="d26">SHALL_NOT_APPLY_TO</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">This exclusion shall not apply to loss or damage caused in the course of reinstating or replacing an otherwise insured damage.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:acceptance_of_new_property_hereon_other_than_as_provided_under_extension_capital_additions_newly_acquired_property_interests" target="ent:satisfactory_completion_of_mechanical_completion_including_testing" id="e:rel:e7b1c692054fdcd9">
  <data key="d26">IS_SUBJECT_TO</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">Acceptance of new property hereon - other than as provided under extension (Capital Additions/ Newly acquired Property/Interests) - is subject to satisfactory completion of the following procedures: Mechanical completion including testing.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:acceptance_of_new_property_hereon" target="ent:satisfactory_completion_of_testing_and_commissioning_conforming_to_100_one_hundred_per_cent_contract_design_to_temperatures_and_pressures_maintained_by_the_entire_plant_in_a_stable_and_controlled_manner_for_a_continuous_ongoing_period_of_a_minimum_of_72_hours_duration" id="e:rel:4352af7cda9f3df3">
  <data key="d26">IS_SUBJECT_TO</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">(a) Testing and commissioning conforming to 100% (one hundred per cent) Contract Design to temperatures and pressures maintained by the entire plant in a stable and controlled manner for a continuous ongoing period of a minimum of 72 hours duration all as approved by the Insured and an engineer firm or licenser involved in said project or as per standard practice of the contractor or the licensor.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:acceptance_of_new_property_hereon" target="ent:satisfactory_completion_of_official_acceptance_by_the_insured_following_formal_handover_without_reservation_or_waiver_of_guarantee_conditions_to_suppliers_of_equipment" id="e:rel:02445502afa69de0">
  <data key="d26">IS_SUBJECT_TO</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">(b) Official acceptance by the Insured following formal handover without reservation or waiver of guarantee conditions to suppliers of equipment in respect of said mechanical specifications it being understood that no equipment faults or punch list items affecting mechanical integrity of the plant are outstanding and that no temporary structures and no modifications remain as shall be notified by the Insured</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:in_the_event_that_compliance_with_a_and_b_above_will_be_deferred_upon_mechanical_completion_and_testing" target="ent:advise_the_insurers_in_writing_of_such_alternative_procedures_which_will_be_adopted_prior_to_the_attachment_hereunder_of_such_new_property" id="e:rel:3e321463216a2320">
  <data key="d26">THE_INSURED_AGREES_TO</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">In the event that compliance with (a) and (b) above will be deferred upon mechanical completion and testing the Insured agrees to advise the Insurers in writing of such alternative procedures which will be adopted prior to the attachment hereunder of such new property</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:acquisitions_exceeding_the_sum_noted_in_the_schedule_of_property_and_plant_hereon" target="ent:insurer_s" id="e:rel:68701bcf06772d62">
  <data key="d26">ARE_TO_BE_AGREED_BY</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">Notwithstanding the above, in respect of acquisitions exceeding the sum noted in the Schedule of property and plant hereon, these are to be agreed by Insurers.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:the_terms_and_conditions_for_acquisitions" target="ent:insurer_s" id="e:rel:9a0e789394a9b96d">
  <data key="d26">ARE_TO_BE_REVIEWED_BY</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">It is further noted and agreed that the terms and conditions are to be reviewed by Insurers.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:the_above_provisions_testing_and_commissioning_clause" target="ent:normal_routine_maintenance_activities_and_scheduled_turnarounds" id="e:rel:64d245268bda4023">
  <data key="d26">DO_NOT_APPLY_TO</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">The above provisions do not apply to normal routine, maintenance activities and scheduled turnarounds.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:for_damage_which_can_be_repaired" target="ent:the_cost_necessarily_incurred_to_restore_the_damaged_item_to_its_former_state_of_serviceability" id="e:rel:bad72c6109a4a10e">
  <data key="d26">THE_BASIS_OF_LOSS_SETTLEMENT_UNDER_SECTION_II_IS</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">For damage which can be repaired, the cost necessarily incurred to restore the damaged item to its former state of serviceability plus the cost of dismantling and re-erection incurred for the purpose of effecting the repairs as well as ordinary freight to and from a repair shop, customs duties and dues, if any, to the extent that such expenses have been included in the Sum Insured.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:cost_to_restore_damaged_item" target="ent:the_cost_of_dismantling_and_re_erection_incurred_for_the_purpose_of_effecting_the_repairs" id="e:rel:764c9ac8bba7804c">
  <data key="d26">PLUS</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">plus the cost of dismantling and re-erection incurred for the purpose of effecting the repairs as well as ordinary freight to and from a repair shop, customs duties and dues, if any, to the extent that such expenses have been included in the Sum Insured.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:cost_to_restore_damaged_item" target="ent:ordinary_freight_to_and_from_a_repair_shop_customs_duties_and_dues_if_any_to_the_extent_that_such_expenses_have_been_included_in_the_sum_insured" id="e:rel:f851cf735da52cba">
  <data key="d26">PLUS</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">plus the cost of dismantling and re-erection incurred for the purpose of effecting the repairs as well as ordinary freight to and from a repair shop, customs duties and dues, if any, to the extent that such expenses have been included in the Sum Insured.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:if_the_repairs_are_carried_out_at_a_workshop_owned_by_the_insured" target="ent:the_cost_of_materials_and_wages_incurred_for_the_purpose_of_the_repairs_plus_a_reasonable_percentage_to_cover_overhead_charges" id="e:rel:bcf1190e9a3a7aa3">
  <data key="d26">THE_INSURER_SHALL_PAY</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">If the repairs are carried out at a workshop owned by the Insured, the Insurer shall pay the cost of materials and wages incurred for the purpose of the repairs plus a reasonable percentage to cover overhead charges.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:no_deduction" target="ent:depreciation_in_respect_of_parts_replaced" id="e:rel:ada883374660c21f">
  <data key="d26">SHALL_BE_MADE_FOR</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">No deduction shall be made for depreciation in respect of parts replaced.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
<edge source="ent:if_the_cost_of_repairs_equals_or_exceeds_the_actual_value_of_the_damaged_property_insured_immediately_before_the_occurrence_of_loss_or_damage" target="ent:constructive_total_loss" id="e:rel:664a0e1b2901c9a0">
  <data key="d26">THAT_PROPERTY_INSURED_SHALL_BE_REGARDED_AS_A</data>
  <data key="d36">0.98</data>
  <data key="d37">sent:tmp_1769774017427_Large_Risk_-_Policy_Wordings:0</data>
  <data key="d38">If the cost of repairs equals or exceeds the actual value of the damaged Property Insured immediately before the occurrence of loss or damage, that Property Insured shall be regarded as a constructive total loss.</data>
  <data key="d29">oneshot</data>
</edge>
</graph></graphml>